name: Supernatural [Tumblr tab icons]
description: "Supernatural icon bar for tumblr. (Impala, KAZ 2Y5, samulet, anti possession tattoo)"
additional_info:
2014-12-10 Tumblr added a new "Explore" tab icon on 2014.12.09, removed the "Logout" tab icon, changed the "Settings" tab icon into the "Account" drop-down menu, and rearranged the icon order. "Home", "Inbox", and "Help" keep their same Supernatural tab icons, "Account" uses the anti-possession sigil, and "Explore" uses Tumblr's default icon.

From style 72597 by user 157267.
